    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for over the years. It runs like a dream and is perfect for anyone looking for a reliable, stylish car without the brand-new price tag. I've loved every mile in it, and I'm sure you will too! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
