    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a perfect balance of luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though I have noted a few minor cosmetic stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the smoke-free cabin features well-preserved leather upholstery with no tears or heavy creasing, and every electronic component\u2014from the premium sound system to the heated seats\u2014is fully operational. Under the hood, the vehicle is mechanically sound, benefiting from a documented history of on-time synthetic oil changes and a recent professional brake service. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains firm and quiet over bumps. It currently rides on premium all-season tires with plenty of tread depth left. This is a solid, honest car that drives as well as it looks. Clear title in hand and ready for a new home.",
      "price": 34500.0,
